## TODO: Generate Real Icons

### Option 1: Quick Online Tool (5 minutes)
1. Go to: https://www.pwabuilder.com/imageGenerator
2. Upload a 512x512 PNG logo
3. Download generated icons
4. Replace all files in this folder

### Option 2: Use ImageMagick (Local)
Run this PowerShell script from this directory:

```powershell
# Requires ImageMagick: choco install imagemagick

$sizes = @(16, 32, 72, 96, 128, 144, 152, 192, 384, 512)
foreach ($size in $sizes) {
    magick convert icon.svg -resize "${size}x${size}" "icon-${size}x${size}.png"
    Write-Host "✅ icon-${size}x${size}.png"
}
```

### Option 3: Manual (Figma/Photoshop)
1. Design logo 512x512px
2. Export as PNG for each size
3. Save with naming: `icon-{size}x{size}.png`

